title: Bonewerkz - 7 Ways to Fly EP (2015)
description:
To all Cypress Hill fans, DJ Muggs fans, B-real fans and Hip Hop fans !


"7 Ways to Fly EP" is containing 7+ instrumentals for reaching the most blunted-smoked-stoned experience since Cypress Hill, since DJ Muggs golden era. You'll dig this.

Produced by Tetrapak Prodzekt
Mixed & Mastered by Tetrapak Prodzekt
Arranged by - Tetrapak Prodzekt & Drama Delight
Scratch - DJ Munja
Cover - Drama Delight
Photo - Marko Lazarevic
Animation - Bonewerkz
